OL,3,GEast Midlands
OL,4,
OL,5,CThis Evening and Tonight:FA fine
OL,6,Fevening, with some late sunshine. Most
OL,7,Fparts staying dry overnight, however
OL,8,Fareas of low cloud and coastal mist
OL,9,Fare expected to spread westwards from
OL,10,Fthe North Sea overnight, perhaps
OL,11,Fbringing the odd spot of light drizzle.
OL,12,
OL,13,CTuesday:FA cloudy start for many, but
OL,14,Fsimilar to Monday, this cloud will
OL,15,Fburn away through the morning to leave
OL,16,Fanother largely sunny day. Very warm
OL,17,Fagain.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
