OL,3,GEast Midlands
OL,4,
OL,5,COutlook for Wednesday to Friday:
OL,6,FLargely dry but breezy, with cloud
OL,7,Fmoving inland overnight then burning
OL,8,Faway by day to give sunny spells.
OL,9,FTemperatures above average for most,
OL,10,Fperhaps very warm for some.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
